16:24.274 --> 16:25.693
<i>that has inspired this theme.</i>

16:25.693 --> 16:27.653
And that's very much what
it's like working with Gustavo.

16:27.653 --> 16:29.154
It's like starting with a lot

16:29.154 --> 16:31.115
and then continuing
to trim it down, trim it down,

16:31.115 --> 16:34.118
and find the right elements
and how they fit.

