19:17.656 --> 19:19.658
<i>And they're in the car,</i>

19:19.658 --> 19:21.493
<i>and you can watch everything,</i>

19:21.493 --> 19:24.204
<i>what's happening
from Sarah's perspective.</i>

19:24.204 --> 19:26.039
WANG: <i>The amazing thing
with that scene</i>

19:26.039 --> 19:28.500
is that it's very true
to the game.

19:28.876 --> 19:32.254
<i>We feel like we're with Sarah
and Joel</i>

19:32.254 --> 19:34.256
<i>in Tommy's truck
the entire time.</i>

19:34.715 --> 19:37.801
And because of our desire
working 360,

19:37.801 --> 19:40.137
<i>it was a big challenge
how should we do that.</i>

