20:13.211 --> 20:15.422
<i>This was nothing but grass.</i>

20:15.422 --> 20:17.299
Craig wrote
this amazing sequence

20:17.299 --> 20:18.884
where our cast,

20:18.884 --> 20:23.305
<i>they walk their way onto this
