So at that point,
we actually opened this up

20:32.981 --> 20:34.775
into the main road behind,

20:34.775 --> 20:37.110
and that gave us
all that extra distance

20:37.110 --> 20:39.446
out there in the real world,
on a real road

20:39.446 --> 20:41.281
for the convoy
to get up to speed

20:41.281 --> 20:42.282
and start chasing them.

