<i>We had to reinforce the plow</i>

20:54.836 --> 20:56.463
<i>because the first night,
it broke.</i>

20:59.299 --> 21:01.927
<i>And then it was the driving
into the house</i>

21:02.844 --> 21:05.013
without destroying the building

21:05.013 --> 21:07.975
because the building
was prepped for fire.

21:07.975 --> 21:11.019
<i>Meaning that post-crash,
we would pull the truck out</i>

21:11.019 --> 21:14.856
<i>and put another truck in there
