21:15.482 --> 21:17.484
Special effects did
an amazing job

21:17.484 --> 21:20.487
<i>piping those houses and vehicles
with propane,</i>

21:20.487 --> 21:23.782
<i>but we'll go in there and
just add the finishing touches.</i>

21:26.827 --> 21:28.453
NOWLAN: <i>In the big,
climactic battle scene,</i>

21:28.453 --> 21:30.998
<i>most of that
was done practically</i>

21:30.998 --> 21:32.332
<i>with real performers.</i>

21:33.083 --> 21:36.336
However, we felt like we needed
to triple that amount.

21:36.336 --> 21:40.173
<i>So, everything in addition
was visual effects.</i>

21:40.507 --> 21:42.718
When we need to make
these creatures in CG,

21:42.718 --> 21:44.636
<i>it's always good to have
a reference</i>

21:44.636 --> 21:47.055
<i>from the actual performers themselves,</i>

