of characters.

21:54.813 --> 21:56.398
<i>We did a mocap session,</i>

21:56.398 --> 21:59.192
<i>tried to record as many
different movements</i>

21:59.192 --> 22:01.445
<i>from the stuntmen
as we possibly could.</i>

22:01.445 --> 22:03.947
<i>We had multiple cameras set up.</i>

22:04.281 --> 22:07.576
WANG: <i>So much of what we do
in post with animation</i>

22:07.576 --> 22:09.202
<i>depends on the performances.</i>

22:09.202 --> 22:11.580
<i>We shot a library
of their movements,</i>

22:11.580 --> 22:14.082
<i>and we selected the best ones
