22:21.256 --> 22:24.551
NOWLAN: <i>Of course, we try to do
as much practically as possible.</i>

22:24.551 --> 22:27.220
<i>The makeup people
were awesome.</i>

22:29.306 --> 22:32.559
The design work
from Barrie Gower's team
was complete.

22:33.101 --> 22:35.062
<i>We took these designs
and we scanned them,</i>

22:35.062 --> 22:38.273
<i>and this helped create
visual assets for us in post.</i>

22:41.151 --> 22:42.486
GOWER: <i>With the infected,</i>

22:42.486 --> 22:44.946
<i>we started exploring all these
other paint schemes.</i>

22:45.530 --> 22:47.240
SPATERI: <i>Once we knew
what the colors were,</i>

22:47.240 --> 22:49.743
<i>then we would paint a suit
to match.</i>

22:49.743 --> 22:52.037
<i>We would glue all the mushrooms
