Each clicker is designed individually.

23:07.594 --> 23:08.970
And the costume
had to be durable enough

23:08.970 --> 23:14.017
<i>to go through all of the crazy
contortionist sort of moves</i>

23:14.017 --> 23:16.269
<i>that the clickers have
in the fight scenes.</i>

23:17.479 --> 23:18.980
STEVE HOLLOWAY:
<i>Then they run through
the breakdown department,</i>

23:18.980 --> 23:21.108
<i>so it looks like they've been
rotting and molding</i>

