<i>with the prosthetics</i>

23:25.529 --> 23:28.406
<i>and the sort of muddy, drippy
costume that's coming off them,</i>

23:28.406 --> 23:30.158
it just looks so amazing.

23:30.408 --> 23:32.452
CYNTHIA SUMMERS: <i>You never
go into battle with one costume,</i>

23:32.452 --> 23:33.537
<i>but these guys did.</i>

